      "widgets_values": [
        "seamless tileable wet cobblestone pavement texture,\northographic top-down bird's eye view, 90 degrees overhead,\nno perspective, no vanishing point, no horizon line,\nflat projection, stones same size across entire image,\ndark grey and charcoal stone surface,\ndeep midnight blue and teal tones in gaps between stones,\nsubtle warm amber tint on stone surfaces,\nLeonid Afremov inspired color palette,\npainted in oil, visible brushstrokes,\nmoderate texture depth, subtle impasto,\nflat diffuse color only, no specular highlights,\nno light reflections, no glossy shine, no bright spots,\nmatte surface appearance, PBR diffuse map,\nflat even illumination, no directional light,\nno focal point, evenly distributed repeating pattern,\nno border, no frame, no vignette,\ntexture fills entire image edge to edge,\nseamless tileable, no visible seams"
